<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        notumalar varaiviṉkaṇ tōḻi cevilikku aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu </p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          The confidant standing with to truth to the foster mother, at [the time of] strangers [making] a marriage [proposal. </p>
         </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="poemXX">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai puṉṉai</l>
<l>poṉṉiṟam viriyum pūkkeḻu tuṟaivaṉai</l>
<l>yeṉṉai yeṉṟum yāmē yivvūr</l>
<l>piṟitoṉ ṟākak kūṟu</l>
<l>māṅku mākkumō vāḻiya pālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
       <l> Oh mother, please mother</l>
      <l>We would say about the man from the ghat abundant with flowers</l>
      <l>That bloom golden-hued [on] the Puṉṉai, ‘[He is] our Lord’.</l>
      <l>This village in unision says something else.</l>
      <l>Will it happen/Is it right that way? May fate live long!</l>
              </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
